{"tid":559985,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"美國隊長盾牌易手疑戰死　寒冬戰士：有可能換我","createTime":"2018-02-13T16:26:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T02:22:43.000Z","uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"aef5e675856c34c5b9cb176f342e0e3dd14a57df","tid":559985,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T16:26:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/電影/159244/-復仇者聯盟-美國隊長盾牌易手疑戰死-寒冬戰士-有可能換我\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%2F159244%2F-%E5%BE%A9%E4%BB%87%E8%80%85%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%8A%E9%95%B7%E7%9B%BE%E7%89%8C%E6%98%93%E6%89%8B%E7%96%91%E6%88%B0%E6%AD%BB-%E5%AF%92%E5%86%AC%E6%88%B0%E5%A3%AB-%E6%9C%89%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%8F%9B%E6%88%91&d=DyFP53Hn%2F%2F%2BzStwfSKSx2wHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=abc2cae6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/電影/159244/-復仇者聯盟-美國隊長盾牌易手疑戰死-寒冬戰士-有可能換我</a><br />\n<br />\n首部黑人超英片《黑豹》（Black Panther）映期進入倒數，早前率先美國獲得極好評，香港未上映已成為一大熱話，不過也不要忘了預計5月在港公映《復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰》，美國隊長的死幾乎已成定局，至於是否真的有人接盾，「寒冬戰士」Sebastian Stan近日接受訪問，疑似證實了美漫迷的推測。"},{"pid":"6d2fd8391e945cbc96f010f98330472be72ea0d2","tid":559985,"uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T16:27:05.000Z","msg":"史上最強Marvel超英片《復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰》（Avengers：Infinity War）由宣布開拍起已成為熱話，特別是有部分最受歡迎的角色將會迎來惡耗，令觀眾愈等愈肉緊。而頭號目標「美國隊長」的死相信已毫無懸念，不止演員Chris Evans的合約已到期，導演羅素兄弟亦親證他不會再演，令粉絲由估邊個死轉場去估邊個接手坐美國隊長個位。<br />\n<br />\n當中最被看好的「寒冬戰士」Bucky，演員Sebastian Stan日前受訪時也直認不諱，「我當然很期待那一日的來臨，不知道會是什麼時候，但將會是個非常不一樣的美國隊長。而且，要把那麼大的責任交到寒冬戰士手上也需要些時間，所以我想是有可能的，只是要令其變得合理。」"},{"pid":"de1df38d8753bc74a64dd0ac2b9b6a423ba5006f","tid":559985,"uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T16:27:22.000Z","msg":"原著漫畫由寒冰戰士接棒<br />\n<br />\n原著中，Steve Rogers在Civil War後被殺，漫畫《Captain America：Volume 34》講述Bucky則接手做新美國隊長，不過經過幾十年作為被洗腦的「寒冬戰士」殺人無數，他要接棒無論心理和生理都將面臨苦戰。在上集《復仇者聯盟》電影中，美國隊長放下盾牌，象徵Steve Rogers已想通作為美國隊長的責任跟他的理念相左，於是決定放下這重身份，接下來將如何呈現美國隊長的交接令人期待。"},{"pid":"50b0f943034a1926c295eb997e104f520990bfd5","tid":559985,"uid":16635,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T16:32:10.000Z","msg":"hk01<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔講以為佢係編劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d2b12f0518980e76d70af018a78f75c985314d","tid":559985,"uid":60023,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T17:44:51.000Z","msg":"要死都唔係今集死啦班濕鳩記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n已成定局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6966014acd692f8bb041003ef14fe2dbffd015bd","tid":559985,"uid":80566,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T17:56:56.000Z","msg":"AVG4都仲有隊長點會係AVG3死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通淨係返黎演回憶咩"},{"pid":"2dcd8c265c60b6f38b1a4cb353779ad39ccfb053","tid":559985,"uid":33004,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"6966014acd692f8bb041003ef14fe2dbffd015bd","tid":559985,"uid":80566,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T17:56:56.000Z","msg":"AVG4都仲有隊長點會係AVG3死<img src=\"/assets/faces/